unittitle_ssm: Brooklyn Collegiate and Polytechnic Institute collection
abstract_ssm: A collection of materials from the Brooklyn Collegiate and Polytechnic Institute, founded in 1854, and the institutions that subsequently grew from it: the Polytechnic Institute of Brooklyn (later the Polytechnic Institute of New York and then Polytechnic University) and Polytechnic Preparatory (Poly Prep).
